& [ReviewArtifactSynthesisDesign] is the design contract for deterministic review evidence drafts from update records
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T09:08:00Z
  @ [update_record] coordination/narrative_coverage_update_record.sop
  @ [review_writer_design] coordination/narrative_append_review_writer_design.sop
  @ [append_cli] scripts/narrative-append.ps1

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is deterministic_review_draft_not_live_deliberation
  + [primary_goal] is reduce hand-authored review fields by deriving deterministic draft review artifacts from a NarrativeCoverageUpdateRecord
  + [non_goal] is claiming Manager or Shaliach semantic approval
  + [non_goal] is applying narrative updates
  + [non_goal] is suppressing residual risks or required rework
  + [non_goal] is replacing local model deliberation once serving is available

& [SynthesisInputs] is the required evidence for deterministic drafts
  + [required_ref] is NarrativeCoverageUpdateRecord artifact
  + [required_value] is current_frontier
  + [optional_value] is manager_residual_risk repeated value
  + [optional_value] is shaliach_finding repeated value
  + [optional_value] is checked_protocol repeated value
  + [authority_boundary] is update_record_fields_not_semantic_review
  = must: derive approved_update_count from appended_update_count
  = must: choose blocked Manager approval when appended_update_count is zero
  = must: include residual risk stating deterministic draft requires real review
  = must: choose Shaliach rework_required when deferred updates exist
  = must: include checked protocols in Shaliach draft

& [ManagerDraftPolicy] is the deterministic Manager review draft rule
  + [approved_status] is approved_for_narrative_append when appended_update_count is greater than zero
  + [blocked_status] is blocked_pending_review when appended_update_count is zero
  + [required_residual_risk] is deterministic_draft_requires_manager_review
  + [authority_boundary] is manager_draft_not_manager_decision
  = must: never approve more updates than the update record appends
  = must: preserve update_record_ref

& [ShaliachDraftPolicy] is the deterministic Shaliach review draft rule
  + [clear_status] is clear_for_narrative_append when deferred_update_count is zero
  + [rework_status] is rework_required_for_narrative_append when deferred_update_count is greater than zero
  + [required_finding] is deterministic_draft_requires_shaliach_review
  + [authority_boundary] is shaliach_draft_not_shaliach_clearance
  = must: convert deferred updates into required_rework entries
  = must: preserve checked protocols
  = must: preserve update_record_ref

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is Manager draft approval count equals appended_update_count
  + [test_case] is Manager draft blocks empty update records
  + [test_case] is Shaliach draft clears when no deferred updates exist
  + [test_case] is Shaliach draft requires rework when deferred updates exist
  + [test_case] is generated drafts carry deterministic-review-not-live-deliberation boundaries

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add pure Manager and Shaliach review draft builders
  + [slice_2] is add optional CLI synthesis mode that writes both artifacts under explicit output refs
  + [slice_3] is refresh checkpoint and audit after synthesis support
